---
title: Southern Pork Chops with White BBQ Sauce, Buttery Corn and Crispy Potatoes
description: Deliciously seared pork chops are a match made in heaven for creamy, buttery corn and a zingy white BBQ sauce. This Southern-style BBQ sauce is mayo-based with a kick of horseradish!
